Pseudorhombus elevatus Ogilby, 1912: 45
( type locality: Bulwer, Moreton Bay, Queensland , Australia );
Chabanaud 1929: 376
(Nha Trang, Vietnam ; listed);
Punpoka 1964: 23
, fig. 5 (Gulf of Thailand ; description);
Shen 1983: 9
, fig. 8 ( Taiwan ; short description);
